g.text: Exercise 1: Data Access
In this exercise you access data available in different file types. The data that you read in this exercise is stored in the "data" folder.
Access the data coming from two customer information systems in .table and .csv formats
Read the file CustomerInfoSystem1.csv (CSV Reader node)
Read the file CustomerInfoSystem2.table (Table Reader node)
Access the data on online orders and product prizes stored on a database
Connect to the Transactions.sqlite database (SQLite Connector node)
Select the "TransactionsOnline" table on the database (DB Table Selector node)
Select the "ProductNrAndPrize" table on the database (DB Table Selector node)
Read the "ProductNrAndPrize" into KNIME (DB Reader)
Optional
Access the data on onsite purchases and the locations of the stores in .xlsx and .table formats
Read the file Stores.xlsx (Excel Reader (XLS) node)
Read the file TransactionsStore.table (Table Reader node)
